            The <strong>Yale</strong> School of Management, also known as <strong>Yale</strong> SOM, is a world-renowned business school that offers MBA, EMBA, MAM, MMS, PhD, Executive Education, and Joint Degree programs.
    </p>

                    <p class="snippet-description">
            March 18, 2004 -
            The <strong>Yale</strong> or Centicore (Latin: Eale) is a mythical beast found in European mythology and heraldry. The <strong>Yale</strong> is described as an antelope- or goat-like creature with the tusks of a boar and large horns. These horns possess the ability to swivel in any direction which makes them good for both offensive ...
    </p>

  }

    align-items: center;
    gap: 6px;
  }

  footer .block a.flex-row > .icon {
    --size: 15px;
  }
</style>
